            src={coffeeNYCCounterCulture}
            alt=`Brendon Smith and Kent Langston at the 2017 New York Coffee Festival
              Counter Culture booth`
            formats={PICTURE_FORMATS}
            class:list={["img-thumbnail"]}
            decoding="async"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p>
            I like to start my days with <a
              href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Specialty_coffee"
              rel="external"
              target="_blank">specialty coffee</a
            >. I frequently hang out at coffee shops around Boston and
            Cambridge. Let me know if you'd like to join me.
          </p>
          <h3>Fitness</h3>
          <Picture
            src={fitnessTrackMeet}
            alt="Brendon Smith competing in a track meet in 2002"
            formats={PICTURE_FORMATS}
            class:list={["img-thumbnail"]}
            decoding="async"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <Picture
            src={fitnessPullUps}
            alt="Brendon Smith doing pull-ups"
            formats={PICTURE_FORMATS}
            class:list={["img-thumbnail"]}
            decoding="async"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p>
            I got into fitness at the beginning of high school. I ran track, and
            got into swimming and strength training. My fitness pursuits taught
            me the value of consistency and focus, and helped me develop an
            active lifestyle that I continue today.
          </p>
          <h3>Movies</h3>
          <Picture
            src={bladeRunnerEye}
            alt="Close-up from Blade Runner (1982) of an eye with the 'Hades Landscape' reflected in the iris"
            formats={PICTURE_FORMATS}
            class:list={["img-thumbnail"]}
            decoding="async"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p>I like collecting and watching movies.</p>
          <p>Here are some of my favorite genres:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Film Noir (<a
                href="https://www.themoviedb.org/keyword/9807-film-noir/movie"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">TheMovieDB</a
              >, <a
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Film_noir"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">Wikipedia</a
              >)
            </li>
            <li>
              Horror (<a
                href="https://www.themoviedb.org/genre/27-horror/movie"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">TheMovieDB</a
              >, <a
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Horror_film"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">Wikipedia</a
              >)
            </li>
            <li>
              Sci-Fi (<a
                href="https://www.themoviedb.org/genre/878-science-fiction/movie"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">TheMovieDB</a
              >, <a
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science_fiction_film"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">Wikipedia</a
              >)
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>Here are some of my favorite directors:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              John Carpenter (<a
                href="https://www.themoviedb.org/person/11770-john-carpenter"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">TheMovieDB</a
              >, <a
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Carpenter"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">Wikipedia</a
              >)
            </li>
            <li>
              Jules Dassin (<a
                href="https://www.themoviedb.org/person/14227-jules-dassin"
                rel="external"
                target="_blank">TheMovieDB</a
              >, <a
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jules_Dassin"
